title: Who's Your Daddy! takes Manhattan
desc: The New York debut of acappella ass-kickers, Who's Your Daddy! will take place December 7th at the legendary Bitter End in Greenwich Village. ?This must see event features  Adam Gorgoni, Freddy Curci, Rick Neigher & Bill New  performing their unique show with singing, banging, clapping and lots of laughing. The show is at 7PM. Also,we are proud to announce that we have been asked by the fine people at Madison Square Garden to sing the National Anthem at the Knicks-Nets game Friday December 4th, and at the Rangers-Ottowa game Sunday December 6th. Anyone who wishes to come witness either of these historic events please contact us for tickets at: wydrecords@gmail.com.? Come on out and see us rock the Garden! ? FAQs Are there ID requirements or an age limit to enter the event? No.? Where can I contact the organizer with any questions? contact: Adam Gorgoni wydrecords@gmail.com ? Is my registration/ticket transferrable? Yes.
